<h1>Newsletter Three</h1>


<h2 id="feature">Feature of the Month:</h2>

<p>Experiment "Sign" button in PDF versions of Experiments.  Now you can click on the "Show PDF Version" of an Experiment, review this PDF version, and then directly sign this PDF version.  This eliminates the step of reviewing a PDF version of an Experiment, clicking on the "Experiment View" button, and returning to Experiment View to sign the Experiment.</p>

<img src="images/image001.png" width="700">

<h2 id="latest_news">New News:</h2>

<p>ArxLab recently unveiled a new user interface that highlights a clean design and modernized pages and dialogue boxes for functions such as logging in, creating new notebooks, and signing Experiments.  In the coming months, Arxspan will be implementing this new look and feel across the entire ArxLab interface.</p>

