<h2 id="recent_enhancements">Recent Enhancements:</h2>

<ol>
<li>
Continued Search Enhancements:  The advanced search interface has a new look and feel; and after submitting any query (chemical structure, generic text, or advanced searches), the hits from your query will be returned more quickly.
<br/>
<img src="images/image005.png" width="224">
<img src="images/image006.png" width="476">
</li>

<li>
Audit Trails in Inventory:  In the Inventory record, for a container of material, there is tracking of who used the substance, when they used it, how much material they subtracted (or added), where the substance in the container came from, and where it has been used.
<br/>
<img src="images/image007.png" width="700">
<img src="images/image008.png" width="700">
</li>

<li>
Integration of ArxLab Assay Registration with ArxLab Notebook: In Result Sets that are generated in ArxLab Assay, there is a new field which allows users to link a Result Set with a particular Experiment in ArxLab Notebook.
<br/>
<img src="images/image009.png" width="700">
</li>

<li>
Integration of ArxLab Assay Registration with ArxLab Registration: In Result Sets that are generated in ArxLab Assay, there is a new field which allows users to link a Result Set with a compound’s Registration page.
<br/>
<img src="images/image010.png" width="700">
</li>

<li>
ArxLab now has enhanced resolution of chemical structures in signed PDF versions of Experiments.
